# File: app/styles/bootstrap.css.ab
# Purpose: Bootstrap 3.3.7 CSS framework — unminified development copy stored in app/styles/
# Dependencies: []

## Overview
Unminified copy of Bootstrap v3.3.7 CSS framework (6757 lines). Provides the same grid system, responsive utilities, components, and styles as `bootstrap.min.css` but in readable, commented form for development inspection. This is the uncompressed counterpart to `app/styles/bootstrap.min.css`.

## Interface
No exports. Reference/development file; the minified version is used in production.

## Dependencies
No project-level dependencies. Vendor file.

## Implementation Notes
- Bootstrap version: 3.3.7 (MIT License)
- 6757 lines unminified
- Identical in content to `app/assets/css/bootstrap.css`
- Kept for developer reference and debugging; the build pipeline uses `bootstrap.min.css` in the output bundle
- Includes the full commented source for all Bootstrap 3 components
